SELECT `uc`.`iUserId` AS `bu_blocked_to`,`uc`.`iConnectionUserId` AS `bu_blocked_by` FROM `user_connections` AS `uc` WHERE (uc.dtAddedAt IS NOT NULL AND uc.dtAddedAt <> '') AND ((uc.iUserId = 11 AND uc.iConnectionUserId = 1) OR (uc.iUserId = 1 AND uc.iConnectionUserId = 11)) AND `uc`.`eConnectionResult` = 'Block'  LIMIT 1

SELECT `m`.`iMessageId` AS `m_message_id` FROM `message` AS `m` WHERE `m`.`iMessageId` = 'S0WLYzxJn7UmwVpne8Tk' OR (m.iSenderId IS NOT NULL AND m.iSenderId <> '') AND (m.iSenderId = 11 AND m.iReceiverId = 1) OR (m.iSenderId = 1 AND m.iReceiverId = 11)  LIMIT 1

SELECT `s`.`iUserId` AS `s_users_id`,`r`.`iUserId` AS `r_users_id`,`r`.`vDeviceToken` AS `r_device_token`,CONCAT(s.vFirstName," ",s.vLastName) AS s_name FROM `message` AS `m` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `s` ON `m`.`iSenderId` = `s`.`iUserId` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `r` ON `m`.`iReceiverId` = `r`.`iUserId` WHERE (m.iSenderId = 11 AND m.iReceiverId = 1)  LIMIT 1
SELECT `n`.`iNotificationId` AS `notification_id` FROM `notification` AS `n` WHERE `iUserId` IN('11') AND `vNotificationMessage` IN('Lara Shah  has sent you a message.') AND `iNotifierId` IN('1')

INSERT INTO `notification` (`vNotificationMessage`, `iNotifierId`, `eNotificationType`, `dtAddedAt`, `dtUpdatedAt`, `eNotificationStatus`, `iUserId`) VALUES ('Lara Shah  has sent you a message.', '1', 'Message', NOW(), NOW(), 'Active', '11')
SELECT `ui`.`vProfileImage` AS `ui_image`,`ui`.`iUserId` AS `ui_users_id` FROM `users` AS `ui` WHERE `ui`.`iUserId` = '11'  LIMIT 1
